snippet: Jordyn Wieber was the official champion of the AT&T American Cup, but Alexandra Raisman and Gabby Douglas also performed well in a display of American depth.
abstract: Jordyn Wieber is the official female gymnastics champion of the AT&T American Cup, but her teammates also performed well in a display of American depth.
lead_paragraph: Jordyn Wieber was the official champion of the AT&T American Cup, but Alexandra Raisman and Gabby Douglas also performed well in a display of American depth.
